Cyber-Knight
The Cyber-Knight is a noble warrior of the highest order: sworn to protect
the innocent, possessing limited psionic ability, and capable of manifesting
a psi-sword of pure mental energy.

Cyber-Knights combine the best physical combat training with minor psionics.
They are among the most respected OCCs on Rifts Earth. Their psi-sword is
impervious to being disarmed and deals Mega-Damage.

Attribute requirements: PS 10, PE 10, MA 10, ME 10.
ISP: Starting ISP pool grants limited psionic use.
Starting equipment: Light armour, horse or riding animal, one ranged weapon,
and an innate psi-sword (manifested psionically).
